# Implementation Plan - Phase 3: Product Listings with Search, Filter, and Pagination

We will implement a complete product catalog system. This includes the database schema for products, a database seed script, a search and filter API on the backend with pagination support, reusable frontend product cards, and catalog navigation pages.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Backend Components

We will create the product schema, query controllers, product routes, and a standalone data seeding script.

#### [NEW] [Product.js](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/backend/models/Product.js)
Defines the schema for product listings including price, image links, stock count, categories, and reviews data.

#### [NEW] [productController.js](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/backend/controllers/productController.js)
Handles queries:
- `getAllProducts`: Search by name matching (`$regex`), filter by category or price range (`$gte`/`$lte`), and slice array for pagination page bounds.
- `getProductById`: Retrieves single product details.
- `createProduct` / `updateProduct` / `deleteProduct`: Admin-protected controllers.

#### [NEW] [productRoutes.js](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/backend/routes/productRoutes.js)
Exposes endpoint routes:
- `GET /api/products` (Public catalog list)
- `GET /api/products/:id` (Public single details)
- `POST /api/products` (Admin-only creation)
- `PUT /api/products/:id` (Admin-only edit)
- `DELETE /api/products/:id` (Admin-only deletion)

#### [NEW] [seed.js](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/backend/seed.js)
A standalone Node script that connects directly to the MongoDB cluster, clears any existing products, and inserts 10 high-quality dummy products.

#### [MODIFY] [server.js](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/backend/server.js)
Mount the product routes under `/api/products`.

---

### Frontend Components

We will build the catalog grid view, detailed pages, loading components, and configure public routing.

#### [NEW] [ProductCard.jsx](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/frontend/src/components/ProductCard.jsx)
A reusable component displaying a product image, name, price tag, category badge, and interactive actions.

#### [NEW] [ProductsPage.jsx](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/frontend/src/pages/ProductsPage.jsx)
The main product feed showing:
- A header search bar.
- Filter panels (drop downs for categories and price thresholds).
- A responsive grid of `ProductCard` items.
- Dynamic page buttons at the bottom for pagination.

#### [NEW] [ProductDetailPage.jsx](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/frontend/src/pages/ProductDetailPage.jsx)
A full layout display shown when clicking a product, rendering descriptions, price, reviews details, stock status, and actions.

#### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///e:/Vishal%20Folder/codex%20intern/Ecommerce%20website/frontend/src/App.jsx)
Configure public routing rules:
- `/` maps to `ProductsPage`.
- `/product/:id` maps to `ProductDetailPage`.
- Maintain login and registration paths.
- Secure user details page under `/dashboard`.

